3T10:03:21.000Z","msg":"嘩，仲有人信呢d"},{"pid":"a4edcd4f7e0cf4c100497c27999460f403faceec","tid":37374,"uid":9531,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T10:05:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>當衝喜囉</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁守孝期間佢係咪唔上得我個邊？<br />\n<br />\n因為我屋企都有老人家<br />\n<br />\n會唔會影響我屋企人？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n依家睇心意既姐，以前就話三兩年，依家通常頭七就完"},{"pid":"b310b02dda82ad0dd71c286a767153605e821b7c","tid":37374,"uid":21249,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T10:06:11.000Z","msg":"你地一齊住定點?<br />\n首先重喪係要隔孝 (即係斷開兩次喪事戴孝時間, 即係唔可以連續戴孝但係兩個先人)<br />\n其二你嫁俾佢習俗上係佢嘅人, 即係你要跟佢守孝<br />\n其三現代守孝著重心意, 守幾耐係你自己定,只要守緊果陣唔好犯禁就得<br />\n<br />\n利申:非殯儀行業"},{"pid":"6f7a1bb821b54423eb1a4387bc59c754f07fd6cf","tid":37374,"uid":38216,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T10:06:31.000Z","msg":"問反屋企的長老啦, 各處鄉村各處例呀"},{"pid":"fd6bf3187021a9f7edabab0215758b92fe305772","tid":37374,"uid":7227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T10:06:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>連登無人做殯儀行業架？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n殯儀仔召喚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n巴打係殯儀仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ？"},{"pid":"25edda8e029715171903418095f2437fbe9fcbd7","tid":37374,"uid":7227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T10:07:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>當衝喜囉</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁守孝期間佢係咪唔上得我個邊？<br />\n<br />\n因為我屋企都有老人家<br />\n<br />\n會唔會影響我屋企人？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n依家睇心意既姐，以前就話三兩年，依家通常頭七就完</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n頭七姐係由過世日計後七日？"},{"pid":"85bf8d25d7751b8dd15692e6ae84e9f10c47228b","tid":37374,"uid":7311,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T10:07:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>當衝喜囉</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁守孝期間佢係咪唔上得我個邊？<br />\n<br />\n因為我屋企都有老人家<br />\n<br />\n會唔會影響我屋企人？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n依家睇心意既姐，以前就話三兩年，依家通常頭七就完</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我今年試過<br />\n<br />\n除咗孝就百無禁忌<br />\n不過你最後叫你未婚夫問清楚 <br />\n做殯儀個班"},{"pid":"8ed2e2fe7b6bbb9b1daa972a0907bf85f08e1343","tid":37374,"uid":1893,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T10:09:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>問反屋企的長老啦, 各處鄉村各處例呀</blockquote><br />\n同意<br />\n其實呢d都係尊重返你既長輩<br />\n問返佢會好啲<br />\n<br />\n如果問唔到既話，我諗就要殯儀既專業人士答你啦"},{"pid":"4310fe3d4671035bff260933e04387774e143ef0","tid":37374,"uid":7227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T10:09:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你地一齊住定點?<br />\n首先重喪係要隔孝 (即係斷開兩次喪事戴孝時間, 即係唔可以連續戴孝但係兩個先人)<br />\n其二你嫁俾佢習俗上係佢嘅人, 即係你要跟佢守孝<br />\n其三現代守孝著重心意, 守幾耐係你自己定,只要守緊果陣唔好犯禁就得<br />\n<br />\n利申:非殯儀行業</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實個時間就好尷尬 <br />\n<br />\n因為我未嫁過去嘅依家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"57e7ebc8117c720e1469e0bb4db34d343661eb4a","tid":37374,"uid":7227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T10:10:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁守孝期間佢係咪唔上得我個邊？<br />\n<br />\n因為我屋企都有老人家<br />\n<br />\n會唔會影響我屋企人？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n依家睇心意既姐，以前就話三兩年，依家通常頭七就完</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我今年試過<br />\n<br />\n除咗孝就百無禁忌<br />\n不過你最後叫你未婚夫問清楚 <br />\n做殯儀個班</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n巴打守孝守左幾耐？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee0b8e409dc4ddb1f0961112aaf9c40c078360ea","tid":37374,"uid":57442,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T10:10:09.000Z","msg":"聽潘聰節目講要百日 唔上得人屋企 因為百日守孝"},{"pid":"22ad27089fd411e9483c4ecf2a172b37eeb4e4ba","tid":37374,"uid":7227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T10:10:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>問反屋企的長老啦, 各處鄉村各處例呀</blockquote><br />\n同意<br />\n其實呢d都係尊重返你既長輩<br />\n問返佢會好啲<br />\n<br />\n如果問唔到既話，我諗就要殯儀既專業人士答你啦</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我父母都好無奈 因為未見過依個情況<br />\n<br />\n佢地叫我上網睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a0e8f4147e35c0816d16012612b9e45aa0892683","tid":37374,"uid":7227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T10:11:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>聽潘聰節目講要百日 唔上得人屋企 因為百日守孝</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n但係我地個囡一百日內會出世<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n咁點算"},{"pid":"db01faf4333bd8255df4eeb2375354790a82c8b6","tid":37374,"uid":42487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T10:12:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>連登無人做殯儀行業架？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n殯儀仔召喚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n巴打係殯儀仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ？</blockquote><br />\nnot me <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 幫手召喚"},{"pid":"d5dfbf805e91a34097b7d41f9bdbfeb62bb3a96d","tid":37374,"uid":7311,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T10:12:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n<br />\n依家睇心意既姐，以前就話三兩年，依家通常頭七就完</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我今年試過<br />\n<br />\n除咗孝就百無禁忌<br />\n不過你最後叫你未婚夫問清楚 <br />\n做殯儀個班</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n巴打守孝守左幾耐？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n火葬完就得<br />\n守孝都冇"},{"pid":"d9ded6ca5235198955ff0419fbe84eb97945dd50","tid":37374,"uid":7227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T10:12:20.000Z","msg":"<b