"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T10:17:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我覺得都係睇返你老公果面屋企人想點就最好<br />\n你係到問左但到最後你老公果面唔LIKE就唔咁好啦</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n老公個邊表示無意見<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f16ed5f33d8d5b01ac50fdad3ae4b07749c8a1b4","tid":37374,"uid":7227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T10:18:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>去紙紮鋪問</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n真係有人答到架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ？"},{"pid":"3f22d74caaa25138c5cb6dbde78df90caf7d4772","tid":37374,"uid":57442,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T10:19:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>聽潘聰節目講要百日 唔上得人屋企 因為百日守孝</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n但係我地個囡一百日內會出世<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n咁點算</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nP.S 我會係娘家坐月</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n果集個殯儀佬係嘉賓 佢話除非係直係親屬，否則盡量唔好去殯儀館，如果非去不可就問殯儀館拎一 set 野 ,辟邪用，正常做殯儀都識，見你大肚會自動比你。之後果1 百日都唔好周圍去。"},{"pid":"c4f92f2d7fc3767457388d7893ea18c07aa1b365","tid":37374,"uid":7227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T10:21:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n<br />\n但係我地個囡一百日內會出世<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n咁點算</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nP.S 我會係娘家坐月</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n果集個殯儀佬係嘉賓 佢話除非係直係親屬，否則盡量唔好去殯儀館，如果非去不可就問殯儀館拎一 set 野 ,辟邪用，正常做殯儀都識，見你大肚會自動比你。之後果1 百日都唔好周圍去。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我個邊就應該唔會比我去<br />\n<br />\n因為孕婦好似唔可以出席依啲場合<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e46506a0e40ceb374550440c9daa220609368a4b","tid":37374,"uid":33234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T10:24:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>有無擺酒？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n睇情況就唔會擺了</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n姐係原本有擺？"},{"pid":"2028592858f6d13f79f1ac3949725cee11942b47","tid":37374,"uid":57442,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T10:24:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n<br />\nP.S 我會係娘家坐月</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n果集個殯儀佬係嘉賓 佢話除非係直係親屬，否則盡量唔好去殯儀館，如果非去不可就問殯儀館拎一 set 野 ,辟邪用，正常做殯儀都識，見你大肚會自動比你。之後果1 百日都唔好周圍去。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我個邊就應該唔會比我去<br />\n<br />\n因為孕婦好似唔可以出席依啲場合<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n有得唔去就盡量唔好去，兩公婆來往應該冇問題既，上朋友屋企就唔好喇。"},{"pid":"38180aeda4af0275483bf631e2052d999d0b471b","tid":37374,"uid":64895,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T10:25:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>是咁的 我同我老公 黎緊平安夜會結婚<br />\n<br />\n但係佢屋企今日有白事 (重喪)<br />\n<br />\n咁佢平時就會上我屋企照顧我 <br />\n<br />\n咁到底佢要守幾耐孝先可以去我屋企？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n一百日？一年？一個月？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 跪求解答</blockquote><br />\n其實通常都睇男方家人既<br />\n不過我之前守左百日"},{"pid":"e359f3fe10f88f50374b4cc5d3e306147d163c19","tid":37374,"uid":32114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T10:27:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>聽潘聰節目講要百日 唔上得人屋企 因為百日守孝</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n但係我地個囡一百日內會出世<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n咁點算</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n忍住啦，盡量唔好生住<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n記住，百日守孝呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c388530db0f0d8080634e8a9ce0c5f9e118b8892","tid":37374,"uid":7227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T10:28:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>有無擺酒？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n睇情況就唔會擺了</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n姐係原本有擺？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n男家本身想擺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f74fc737d0ee26f08c4178a389cf1f43203daf6a","tid":37374,"uid":28960,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T10:28:39.000Z","msg":"之前守百日<br />\n其實都係老一輩話事"},{"pid":"327d1af1b253c327f734ad25fb625048834cae18","tid":37374,"uid":7227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T10:28:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n<br />\n果集個殯儀佬係嘉賓 佢話除非係直係親屬，否則盡量唔好去殯儀館，如果非去不可就問殯儀館拎一 set 野 ,辟邪用，正常做殯儀都識，見你大肚會自動比你。之後果1 百日都唔好周圍去。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我個邊就應該唔會比我去<br />\n<br />\n因為孕婦好似唔可以出席依啲場合<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n有得唔去就盡量唔好去，兩公婆來往應該冇問題既，上朋友屋企就唔好喇。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n姐係男方上女家係可以？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"05779f7103f8fa803a16745e3138a731c3107b10","tid":37374,"uid":4545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T10:29:22.000Z","msg":"好複雜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fbdf32884106ed49a47032383d874792b60364cf","tid":37374,"uid":7227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T10:29:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>是咁的 我同我老公 黎緊平安夜會結婚<br />\n<br />\n但係佢屋企今日有白事 (重喪)<br />\n<br />\n咁佢平時就會上我屋企照顧我 <br />\n<br />\n咁到底佢要守幾耐孝先可以去我屋企？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n一百日？一年？一個月？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 跪求解答</blockquote><br